snippet.title: THE PATHLESS | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Embark on an adventure with your eagle to a mystical island and dispel a curse of darkness that grips the world in The Pathless, available now on PS5, PS4, Epic Games Store, and Apple Arcade. https://thepathless.com/

Physical version available here: https://pathless.iam8bit.com/

Developed by GIANT SQUID. Published by Annapurna Interactive.

© Annapurna Interactive, 2020
